    "English": "A writhing sac of genetic fluid, designed to foster the creation of new <span class=\"name name-technology\">bio-infused technology</span> for a <span class=\"name name-technology\">sentient starship</span>.<br><br>The embryo will grow into <span class=\"name name-technology\">bio-technology upgrade</span>. <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Begin biogenesis</span> with <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>.",
