    "TraditionalChinese": "一個扭動的基因液囊，用來促進<span class=\"name name-technology\">知覺太空船</span>創造新的<span class=\"name name-technology\">生物結合科技</span>。<br><br>胚胎將會成長為<span class=\"name name-technology\">生物科技升級</span>。按下 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 即可<span class=\"name name-stellar\">開始生物合成</span>。"
